metadata.name: Crypto Labs #2
metadata.description: CryptoLabs NFT is a collection of 7777 unique, one-of-a-kind Labrador Puppies living on Ethereum Blockchain. It showcases the playful and loyal nature of the Labrador breed. These PFPs are perfect for fans of Labradors or anyone looking for a cute and charming way to represent themselves online. With so many options, you can find the ideal PFP to suit your personality and style. So come and check out our "CryptoLabs" collection and bring some of the joy and loyalty of the Labrador breed into your digital world.
